# Pack Testdata Fixtures

## Purpose
Provide stable, minimal pack fixtures for TestX invariant tests.

## Invariants
- Fixtures must remain deterministic and JSON-only.
- No executable files are allowed.
- IDs are intentionally simple and namespaced for repeatable tests.
